{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d44aaaa1a0","title":"浙江大学关于政治考试问题的大字报","origin":"浙江大学马列主义教研室资料室编印《右派言论汇编（内部刊物）》，1957年11月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c372023dc8","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ab481de468","type":"title","text":"浙江大学关于政治考试问题的大字报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"9ab03e40c1","type":"subtitle","text":"1、19个班级的联合呼吁！[广播稿]","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"aee7d60e98","type":"paragraph","text":"[此为右派分子盗用19个班的同学名义，进行煽动的广播稿。——编者注——]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"26da2ec967","type":"appellation","text":"同学们：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"7046750feb","type":"paragraph","text":"你们觉得政治考试有必要吗？不，我们19个班级一致认为没有必要，我们的理由是：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"bd28621ea9","type":"paragraph","text":"1、我们认为政治考试完全是教条的统一，除了死背硬记以外还能得到什么呢？","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"fa33281603","type":"paragraph","text":"2、作为重要的技术基础课如“公差”“水力机械”“调整原理”“工业电子学”等课程均可不考，难道政治一定要考吗？","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"b03b0ee6ba","type":"paragraph","text":"3、政治学习是为了提高思想，而“鸣放”是提高思想活生生的教育，我们认为其重要性比政治考试还重要。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"fd46b7e763","type":"paragraph","text":"4、作为重点学校的清华、北大等6、7校可以不考政治，难道我们浙大一定要吗？","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"c68181a514","type":"paragraph","text":"同学们！我们要求立即停止政治考试。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"65f2124c6c","type":"subtitle","text":"2、法宝","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"32241777ad","type":"paragraph","text":"同学们\t都知道，\t\t政治考试臭法宝，\t\t\t引诱同学不足道，","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"9587d79497","type":"paragraph","text":"垃圾堆中可去找，\t\t政治考试又来到，\t\t\t“书呆子”哈哈笑，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"f1fe2bdc4a","type":"paragraph","text":"死记硬背啃教条，\t\t字字句句公式套，\t\t\t品德恶劣吃五分，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"f4d06b4940","type":"paragraph","text":"你说好笑不好笑！！！\t政治学习很重要，\t\t\t红色专家是一套，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"427212620e","type":"paragraph","text":"要是真正学得好，\t\t理行一致何必考，\t\t\t“鸣放”来把决心表，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"01354daef9","type":"paragraph","text":"政治考试快取消，\t\t领导装聋又装哑，\t\t\t我们坚决不罢了，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"1f90254792","type":"paragraph","text":"不罢了，坚决不罢了！！！","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"80d1007b2a","type":"paragraph","text":" 化燃\t551","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"c69b6c0cb0","type":"subtitle","text":"3、揭露","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"15a2ac51b1","type":"paragraph","text":"政治考试是彻头彻尾的教条主义，是校方企图剥夺我们的争鸣时间，我们坚决反对！！！","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"1201897a95","type":"subtitle","text":"4、取消政治考试","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"e5b6623e1b","type":"paragraph","text":"我们完全拥护一些先进班级提出来的取消政治考试的意见，众所周知学习政治的目的，是为了提高思想认识觉悟，但考试的要求又是什么呢？不外乎死记教条，只要能背得出，考试保证不成问题，难道只有把“六大”七届二中……的决议精神一字不差的背出来，思想觉悟就能提高了吗？恰恰相反，要起的积极作用，只不过教条的培养，因此我们坚决反对这种形式主义的政治考试。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"5a93adca36","type":"subtitle","text":"5、政治考试≌教条统一","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"e5d5fd7606","type":"paragraph","text":"我们坚决拥护取消政治考试制度","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"58a3aa3267","type":"paragraph","text":"“重点学校”北大、清华已取消，难道浙大学生一定要考。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"bcaa5cdb2b","type":"paragraph","text":"一、政治考试与百家争鸣的方针是不相容的，要求各人对各种国内外问题要有同样的教条的看法，因而不同的见解丝毫不能发挥，假使发挥就吃2分。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"49c1bb92ef","type":"paragraph","text":"看百家怎么能鸣呢？","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"0babadcc0a","type":"paragraph","text":"二、政治考试成绩的优劣，不能用来衡量一个人的思想品质的好坏，考得好不见得“先进”，考得不好，不见得“落后”，因为只要会背教条，就是5分。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"},{"id":"cdbe59cc15","type":"paragraph","text":"三、政治学习是必要的，它能提高人的思想认识，但考试除了培养人的教条主义外无积极的意义，我们认为思想认识的提高与优良道德品质的培养，是决定于平时的政治的质量。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0"}],"page":{"id":"3e9f921bba","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"d44aaaa1a0","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}